law.catch_line: Filing of rates, underwriting guidelines, evidence of coverage, and changes -- Filing fee.
law.text: Self-insured employer-organized association groups shall file with the commissioner their rates, underwriting guidelines, evidence of coverage, and any changes therein. The filing shall be accompanied by a filing fee of five dollars ($5) per form filing.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1268, effective July 15, 2010. -- Created 2003 Ky. Acts ch. 78, sec. 18, effective June 24, 2003.
